#: ../../source/news/releases/1.0.x/announcing-1.0.6/index.rst:12
msgid ""
"Fix Galley Helm charts so that the ``validatingwebhookconfiguration`` "
"object can now deployed to a namespace other than ``istio-system`` "
"(`Issue 13625 <https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/13625>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.0.x/announcing-1.0.6/index.rst:15
msgid ""
"Additional Helm chart fixes for anti-affinity support: fix "
"``gatewaypodAntiAffinityRequiredDuringScheduling`` and "
"``podAntiAffinityLabelSelector`` match expressions and fix the default "
"value for ``podAntiAffinityLabelSelector`` (`Issue 13892 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/13892>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.0.x/announcing-1.0.6/index.rst:20
msgid ""
"Make Pilot handle a condition where Envoy continues to request routes for"
" a deleted gateway while listeners are still draining (`Issue 13739 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/13739>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.0.x/announcing-1.0.6/index.rst:25
msgid "Small enhancements"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.0.x/announcing-1.0.6/index.rst:27
msgid ""
"If access logs are enabled, ``passthrough`` listener requests will be "
"logged."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.0.x/announcing-1.0.6/index.rst:29
msgid ""
"Make Pilot tolerate unknown JSON fields to make it easier to rollback to "
"older versions during upgrade."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.0.x/announcing-1.0.6/index.rst:31
msgid ""
"Add support for fallback secrets to ``SDS`` which Envoy can use instead "
"of waiting indefinitely for late or non-existent secrets during startup "
"(`Issue 13853 <https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/13853>`_)."
msgstr ""

